              // from PlatformConfig\n  treasury: PublicKey,\n  \n  // Computed during settlement:\n  pool: bigint = entryAmount * 2n,\n  feeAmount: number = (pool * feeBps) / 10_000n,\n  payoutAmount: number = pool - feeAmount,\n  resultHash: Buffer (SHA256),\n  resultSide: number (0 or 1),\n  winner: PublicKey\n}\n```\n\n#### Lord of RNGs: `settleLordRound(deps, pda)`\n**Available fields at settlement time**:\n```javascript\n{\n  entries: Array<{\n    player: PublicKey,\n    amountLamports: bigint\n  }>,\n  totalAmountLamports: bigint,\n  algorithmVer: number,\n  feeBps: number,\n  treasury: PublicKey,\n  \n  // Computed during settlement:\n  feeAmount: number = (totalAmountLamports * feeBps) / 10_000n,\n  payoutAmount: number = totalAmountLamports - feeAmount,\n  rentRefund: number,\n  winningOffset: bigint,\n  winnerEntryIndex: number,\n  winner: PublicKey\n}\n```\n\n### Database Updates at Settlement\nBoth games call:\n1. `db.updateRoundPhase(pda, \"settled\", { settle_tx, result_hash, result_side, winner, settle_attempts })`\n2. `db.updateRoundEntries(pda, entries)` — stores serialized array to `rounds.entries` JSONB column\n3. `db.insertOperatorEvent(pda, \"settle_confirmed\", {...})` — logs event details including fee/payout breakdown\n4. `db.insertTransaction({ wallet, game, matchId, txType: \"payout\", amountLamports, txSig })` — payout transaction record\n\n### Key Fields Available for Referral Processing\n```javascript\n{\n  round_id: string (from rounds.match_id),\n  game_type: string (\"coinflip\" or \"lord\"),\n  wager_lamports: bigint (entry_amount for coinflip, or individual entry amount for lord),\n  fee_lamports: number (feeAmount from settlement calc),\n  payoutAmount: number (for winner),\n  referrer_wallet: string,\n  referee_wallet: string,\n  winner: string\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. Event Queue System\n\n### Event Types (defined in `event-types.ts`)\n```javascript\nEventTypes = {\n  REFERRAL_CODE_APPLIED: \"referral.code_applied\",\n  REFERRAL_